title: 2008-05-05 Joanne Shaw Taylor FLAC, Chiddingfold Club
description:
Band: Joanne Shaw Taylor
Date: 5th May 2008
Venue: Chiddingfold Club, UK

This was probably the last ever gig at this venue which is closing down for redevelopment.

Joanne Shaw Taylor played in support of The Hoax.

Taper: sonicsavage
Giant Squid mics (without the battery box/bass rolloff) -> iRiver HD340 (running rockbox and recording in CD quality wav format) -> Adobe Audition (EQ and normalisation) -> FLAC -> you

Missed the beginning of the first song, which fades in as I came into the hall.
